The '''Grotto City''' was discovered by [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]], [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]], and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] in a grotto far beneath [[Haven Base]] on [[Arbra/Legends|Arbra]]. A magnificent structure, C-3PO identified its architecture as dating to the time of [[Xim/Legends|Xim the Despot]]. The city was the long-abandoned home of the ancient [[Arbran (species)|Arbran]] race. The Arbrans had abandoned their homeworld long ago, but had first shed all their negative emotions in the formation of a [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] manifestation known as the [[Darker]]. As their own offspring, the Arbrans were unwilling to destroy the Darker, and left him in the Grotto City, surrounded by a [[Force screen|self-perpetuating force field]]. In the city, C-3PO found a library with ancient tomes containing everything from cookbooks to history; he observed the writing to be similar to that of the ancient [[Sith (language)|Sith]]. Chewbacca and some [[Hoojib/Legends|Hoojibs]] shoved the Darker into the force field, resulting in the destruction of the Darker, the field, and the entire Grotto City.

